James G. Snitzer https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_G._Snitzer 0 James George Snitzer (1926 – 22 March 1945), also known as Jimmy Snitzer or Jim Snitzer, was an American film actor. He was killed while serving with the United States Army in 1945. James_George_Snitzer ( 1926 – 22_March_1945 ) , also_known as Jimmy_Snitzer or Jim_Snitzer , was an_American_film_actor .
